# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Keep the 3D model assets tracked.
#
# The `*.obj` rule above (under "Object files") is boilerplate for COMPILER
# object files, but it also matches the Wavefront .obj MESH files the renderer
# loads from assets/. Those meshes are real project assets and MUST be
# committed, so re-include them here (a later pattern wins over an earlier one).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
!**/assets/*.obj
!**/assets/**/*.obj
